  return <MDXLayout {...layoutProps} {...props} components={components} mdxType="MDXLayout">

    <p>{`In this section we will understand how to customize node running parameters in `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`devtools/chain/genesis.toml`}</inlineCode>{` which only affect individual nodes in a network. Different nodes can set their own parameters depending on their operation environment.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "overview"
    }}>{`Overview`}</h2>
    <p>{`Let's take a look at `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`devtools/chain/config.toml`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`# crypto
privkey = "0x4a33067c449635c434cc758ed5f595e1f5653debc45233997c93814c31f710d5"

# db config
data_path = "./devtools/chain/data"

[graphql]
listening_address = "0.0.0.0:8000"
graphql_uri = "/graphql"
graphiql_uri = "/graphiql"
workers = 0 # if 0, uses number of available logical cpu as threads count.
maxconn = 25000
max_payload_size = 1048576

[network]
listening_address = "0.0.0.0:1337"
rpc_timeout = 10

[consensus]
sync_txs_chunk_size = 5000

[[network.bootstraps]]
peer_id = "QmeG2AjWkLbK5ThySV7TrX5KuFryPsaM8GBgDs6Ch1Z5xJ"
address = "0.0.0.0:1888"

[mempool]
pool_size = 20000
broadcast_txs_size = 200
broadcast_txs_interval = 200

[executor]
light = false

[logger]
filter = "info"
log_to_console = true
console_show_file_and_line = false
log_path = "logs/"
log_to_file = true
metrics = true
# you can specify log level for modules with config below
# modules_level = { "overlord::state::process" = "debug", core_consensus = "error" }

[rocksdb]
max_open_files = 64

# [apm]
# service_name = "muta"
# tracing_address = "127.0.0.1:6831"
# tracing_batch_size = 50
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Let’s go line-by-line and understand what each parameter means.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "full-list-of-node-running-parameters"
    }}>{`Full list of node running parameters`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "local-parameters"
    }}>{`Local parameters`}</h3>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Parameter`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Description`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Default`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`privkey`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`节点私钥，节点的唯一标识，在作为 bootstraps 节点时，需要给出地址和该私钥对应的公钥让其他节点连接；如果是出块节点，该私钥对应的地址需要在 consensus verifier_list 中`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`data_path`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`链数据所在目录`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "graphql-parameters"
    }}>{`GraphQL parameters`}</h3>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Parameter`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Description`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Default`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`listening_address`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`GraphQL 监听地址`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`graphql_uri`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`GraphQL 服务访问路径`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`graphiql_uri`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`GraphiQL 访问路径`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`workers`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`处理 http 的线程数量，填 0 的话，会默认按 CPU 的核数`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`maxconn`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`最大连接数`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "network-parameters"
    }}>{`Network parameters`}</h2>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Parameter`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Description`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Default`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`listening_address`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`GraphQL 监听地址`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`graphql_uri`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`GraphQL 服务访问路径`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "network-bootstraps-node-parameters"
    }}>{`Network bootstraps node parameters`}</h2>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Parameter`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Description`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Default`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`pubkey`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`公钥`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`address`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`网络地址`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "mempool-parameters"
    }}>{`Mempool parameters`}</h2>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Parameter`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Description`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Default`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`pool_size`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`交易池大小`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`broadcast_txs_size`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`一次批量广播的交易数量`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`broadcast_txs_interval`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`每次广播交易的时间间隔，单位 ms`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "executor-parameters"
    }}>{`Executor parameters`}</h2>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Parameter`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Description`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Default`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`light`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`设为 true 时，节点将只保存最新高度的 state`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "logger-parameters"
    }}>{`Logger parameters`}</h2>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Parameter`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Description`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`Default`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`filter`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`全局日志级别`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`log_to_console`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`是否输出日志到 console，生产环境建议设为 false`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`console_show_file_and_line`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`当 `}<inlineCode parentName="td">{`log_to_console`}</inlineCode>{` 和本配置都置为 true 时，console 输出的日志里会包含日志打印处的文件和行数。本地通过日志调试时有用，一般可以设为 false。`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`log_to_file`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`是否输出日志到文件`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}><inlineCode parentName="td">{`metrics`}</inlineCode></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}>{`是否输出 metrics。logger 模块中有专门的 metrics 输出函数，如有需要，可以用来输出 metrics 日志，不受全局日志级别的影响，且对应的日志会输出到专门的文件。`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": "left"
          }}></td>
        </tr>
